quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  25,33,"Wala ya/toonaka bimathalin illaji/naka bilhaqqi waahsana tafseera"
  25,34,"Allatheena yuhsharoona AAalawujoohihim ila jahannama ola-ika sharrun makananwaadallu sabeela"
  25,35,"Walaqad atayna moosaalkitaba wajaAAalna maAAahu akhahu haroonawazeera"
  25,36,"Faqulna ithhaba ilaalqawmi allatheena kaththaboo bi-ayatinafadammarnahum tadmeera"
  25,37,"Waqawma noohin lamma kaththabooarrusula aghraqnahum wajaAAalnahum linnasiayatan waaAAtadna liththalimeenaAAathaban aleema"
  25,38,"WaAAadan wathamooda waas-habaarrassi waquroonan bayna thalika katheera"
  25,39,"Wakullan darabna lahu al-amthalawakullan tabbarna tatbeera"
  25,40,"Walaqad ataw AAala alqaryati allateeomtirat matara assaw-i afalam yakoonooyarawnaha bal kanoo la yarjoona nushoora"
  25,41,"Wa-itha raawka in yattakhithoonakailla huzuwan ahatha allathee baAAatha Allahurasoola"
  25,42,"In kada layudillunaAAan alihatina lawla an sabarnaAAalayha wasawfa yaAAlamoona heena yarawna alAAathabaman adallu sabeela"
  25,43,"Araayta mani ittakhatha ilahahuhawahu afaanta takoonu AAalayhi wakeela"
